query:
SELECT ar.id, ar.auditInstanceId, ar.questionId, ar.response, ar.textResponse, ar.numberResponse, atq.questionText 
FROM auditResponses ar 
JOIN auditTemplateQuestions atq ON ar.questionId = atq.id 
WHERE ar.auditInstanceId = 150001 
AND atq.questionText LIKE '%All incidents are recorded%'
LIMIT 5
